1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,970 --> 00:01:39,740
[I Don't Want to
Be Friends With You]

3
00:01:42,430 --> 00:01:44,750
[Solidarity and friendship]

4
00:01:44,750 --> 00:01:46,460
I just borrow some money.

5
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:48,020
I'll pay back.

6
00:01:48,229 --> 00:01:48,880
Don't worry.

7
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:49,660
Well...

8
00:01:50,910 --> 00:01:52,060
When will you pay back?

9
00:01:52,420 --> 00:01:54,350
I'll pay back when I like.

10
00:01:54,670 --> 00:01:56,229
Don't ask too much.

11
00:01:58,310 --> 00:01:59,020
Hey, bro.

12
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:00,710
I'll give you money.

13
00:02:03,470 --> 00:02:04,670
Dare you come and get it?

14
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:11,460
You're amazing.

15
00:02:11,460 --> 00:02:13,150
You fought three persons at once.

16
00:02:13,830 --> 00:02:14,710
I tell you what.

17
00:02:15,060 --> 00:02:17,750
People who come to school
to rob money are basically losers.

18
00:02:18,140 --> 00:02:19,750
I learned a few moves from my dad
when I was a kid.

19
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:20,990
It's easy to knock them down.

20
00:02:21,390 --> 00:02:22,190
Chen Jun He,

21
00:02:22,510 --> 00:02:24,390
I, Niu Xiao Huo,
am overwhelmed by you.

22
00:02:25,030 --> 00:02:26,590
We'll take you
as our elder brother from now on.

23
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:27,030
Yes.

24
00:02:27,030 --> 00:02:28,870
You are our elder brother from now on.

25
00:02:29,750 --> 00:02:30,579
Whatever.

26
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:33,710
Could you teach me several moves?

27
00:02:33,710 --> 00:02:35,350
I use it for self-defence.

28
00:02:35,350 --> 00:02:37,329
[Solidarity and friendship]

29
00:02:37,420 --> 00:02:38,920
[Episode 17, The Alliance]

30
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:43,430
What's wrong with you?

31
00:02:44,420 --> 00:02:45,740
Did I do something wrong?

32
00:02:48,380 --> 00:02:50,700
I know I am unreasonable now.

33
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:53,200
We used to be good friends

34
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:55,329
but now I treat you like this.

35
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,829
I don't know how to explain it.

36
00:03:01,230 --> 00:03:02,590
I know you are nice to me

37
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:06,520
and I want to go on with you.

38
00:03:06,990 --> 00:03:09,180
But I have to say you something.

39
00:03:09,300 --> 00:03:11,220
Everything will disappear eventually.

40
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,840
I'm destined to leave.

41
00:03:14,610 --> 00:03:16,660
We'll get nothing at the end.

42
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:20,500
Rather than wait until then
to be upset,

43
00:03:21,190 --> 00:03:22,790
why not end this in advance

44
00:03:23,510 --> 00:03:25,870
to save everyone an awkward situation?

45
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:28,510
Am I right?

46
00:03:29,230 --> 00:03:30,040
No!

47
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,850
What does it mean
to be destined to leave?

48
00:03:32,970 --> 00:03:35,490
I never believe in the word "destiny".

49
00:03:35,790 --> 00:03:37,150
You're just going abroad.

50
00:03:37,579 --> 00:03:39,110
I can be with you anywhere.

51
00:03:39,730 --> 00:03:42,170
I could go with you
to Antarctica if you wanted to.

52
00:03:42,810 --> 00:03:45,100
It's not like you're going
to die or leave the earth.

53
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:47,280
Why is it doomed to be fruitless?

54
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:50,420
If it comes to the time to part,

55
00:03:50,620 --> 00:03:51,460
then I'll accept it.

56
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,230
But now,

57
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:54,760
I don't accept it,

58
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,400
and I can't accept it.

59
00:03:56,910 --> 00:03:58,550
If I'm willing and you're willing,

60
00:03:58,650 --> 00:04:00,850
why can't we just go on?

61
00:04:19,810 --> 00:04:20,690
Double five!

62
00:04:22,490 --> 00:04:24,060
How's your dinner going?

63
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:27,420
Forget about the dinner.

64
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:29,180
I made a new friend.

65
00:04:29,590 --> 00:04:31,090
What new friend?

66
00:04:34,150 --> 00:04:36,130
Do you think she has
fallen in love with someone else?

67
00:04:36,270 --> 00:04:38,190
I've told you to take me to dinner.

68
00:04:38,250 --> 00:04:38,760
See,

69
00:04:38,850 --> 00:04:39,730
you can't handle it.

70
00:04:41,060 --> 00:04:41,890
Just think!

71
00:04:41,980 --> 00:04:43,120
Is there any other way?

72
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:45,390
Since dating doesn't work,

73
00:04:45,730 --> 00:04:46,880
write her a love letter.

74
00:04:46,970 --> 00:04:48,140
Cut the crap.

75
00:04:48,370 --> 00:04:49,760
Write her a love letter?

76
00:04:50,610 --> 00:04:51,909
If I could write love letters,

77
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,909
I wouldn't be in this position.

78
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,200
Double nine.

79
00:04:55,409 --> 00:04:56,420
I write it for you.

80
00:04:58,540 --> 00:04:59,950
You can write love letters?

81
00:05:00,770 --> 00:05:02,690
I don't see you have a girlfriend.

82
00:05:02,780 --> 00:05:04,620
That's because
I don't want to pursue one.

83
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,040
Tomorrow,

84
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:08,010
I'll show you what I can do.

85
00:05:09,350 --> 00:05:10,100
Double two.

86
00:05:18,420 --> 00:05:19,420
Li Qing Tong.

87
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:20,550
Are you asleep?

88
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:24,430
Not yet.

89
00:05:26,470 --> 00:05:27,170
Say it.

90
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:29,600
How's things with Duan Xiao?

91
00:05:31,180 --> 00:05:32,340
Nothing much.

92
00:05:35,930 --> 00:05:37,130
Do you think

93
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:39,650
I am odd at times?

94
00:05:39,930 --> 00:05:41,250
Yes, you're odd.

95
00:05:42,620 --> 00:05:44,100
Why do you have to
keep distance with him

96
00:05:44,190 --> 00:05:46,310
for no reason at all?

97
00:05:47,250 --> 00:05:48,040
Hua.

98
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,360
I have to tell you.

99
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,500
Whatever you think,

100
00:05:51,590 --> 00:05:53,310
you have to make a decision
as soon as possible.

101
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:55,870
People around us are not fools.

102
00:05:55,900 --> 00:05:57,510
Everyone knows that both of you

103
00:05:57,530 --> 00:05:59,220
are not just friends.

104
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,360
You should give him a clear answer,

105
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:03,680
whether you agree or not.

106
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:06,780
I know.

107
00:06:07,450 --> 00:06:08,290
Let's sleep.

108
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,670
You know nothing, you know.

109
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:31,390
Hello!

110
00:06:37,130 --> 00:06:38,540
Do you feel that

111
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:41,220
your eyes are strange today?

112
00:06:41,750 --> 00:06:42,830
What?

113
00:06:43,730 --> 00:06:45,320
It's strangely beautiful.

114
00:06:46,990 --> 00:06:47,870
Thanks.

115
00:06:48,820 --> 00:06:51,020
I didn't think
you would like to talk to me.

116
00:06:51,020 --> 00:06:51,900
Why?

117
00:06:52,580 --> 00:06:53,980
Because I think

118
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:55,990
a beautiful girl like you

119
00:06:55,990 --> 00:06:57,909
won't talk to others easily.

120
00:06:58,470 --> 00:07:00,110
Not exactly.

121
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:09,420
That girl has agreed
to have dinner with me.

122
00:07:09,780 --> 00:07:10,750
Then?

123
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:12,160
You know what I mean.

124
00:07:12,820 --> 00:07:14,010
I can't handle it.

125
00:07:14,380 --> 00:07:15,540
You're just paying lip service.

126
00:07:15,900 --> 00:07:18,010
Communication is useful.

127
00:07:18,150 --> 00:07:20,460
You see, I get along
so well with strangers.

128
00:07:20,460 --> 00:07:22,580
You've known Li Qing tong
for so many years,

129
00:07:22,670 --> 00:07:24,920
can't you take the initiative
to do something she likes?

130
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:28,790
Well, tell me,

131
00:07:29,010 --> 00:07:29,930
what should I do?

132
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:30,930
I have told you.

133
00:07:30,990 --> 00:07:32,260
Write her a love letter.

134
00:07:45,150 --> 00:07:45,900
Hello!

135
00:07:45,990 --> 00:07:47,020
What are you doing?

136
00:07:48,409 --> 00:07:49,730
I'm writing a love letter.

137
00:07:51,909 --> 00:07:53,550
How's the conversation

138
00:07:53,870 --> 00:07:54,900
with the Swift Leg?

139
00:07:56,580 --> 00:07:57,510
It's hard to say.

140
00:07:58,340 --> 00:08:00,070
Why do you
write love letters suddenly?

141
00:08:02,010 --> 00:08:03,630
Fan said,

142
00:08:03,770 --> 00:08:05,990
if you can't say some words in person,

143
00:08:06,220 --> 00:08:07,660
you can write it down.

144
00:08:08,310 --> 00:08:08,780
By the way,

145
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:11,180
have you ever written

146
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:12,270
a love letter?

147
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:13,470
How to write it?

148
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:14,850
Sisters!

149
00:08:15,550 --> 00:08:17,340
What do you think
we come to university for?

150
00:08:20,860 --> 00:08:22,470
I'm talking to you!

151
00:08:24,230 --> 00:08:25,110
Do you want some oranges?

152
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:28,580
Do you think it makes sense
for us to eat and sleep all day?

153
00:08:29,420 --> 00:08:32,370
Shouldn't we
enrich our life after school?

154
00:08:33,690 --> 00:08:34,960
Forget about it!

155
00:08:35,350 --> 00:08:38,110
Will you enrich your life
in class first?

156
00:08:38,110 --> 00:08:40,110
You're the only one in our dorm
who skips class all day.

157
00:08:40,110 --> 00:08:41,950
We all study hard except you.

158
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,780
I'm trying to set a new target.

159
00:08:44,870 --> 00:08:46,230
Leave her alone.

160
00:08:46,310 --> 00:08:48,910
She just wants us
to join the Drama Club.

161
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:50,160
She has nagged this several days.

162
00:08:50,190 --> 00:08:50,980
Bingo!

163
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:53,440
Anyway, I will stop
this relentless nagging

164
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:55,820
only when you guys
give in and agree to join.

165
00:08:56,210 --> 00:08:57,730
Just join it if you like.

166
00:08:57,910 --> 00:08:59,060
Why torture us?

167
00:08:59,070 --> 00:09:00,440
We need to look after each other.

168
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,660
Look at us.

169
00:09:02,020 --> 00:09:03,080
Look at our figure,

170
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,120
and our look.

171
00:09:04,310 --> 00:09:05,980
We are complimented by everyone.

172
00:09:06,990 --> 00:09:08,490
It's a waste not to act.

173
00:09:09,590 --> 00:09:10,990
You are reasonable.

174
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:13,460
You're too easy to fool, aren't you?

175
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:16,270
The problem is that
we don't know how to act.

176
00:09:16,370 --> 00:09:17,180
Don't worry!

177
00:09:17,330 --> 00:09:18,240
Who is born to act?

178
00:09:18,350 --> 00:09:19,300
We can learn there.

179
00:09:19,530 --> 00:09:20,250
Zhang Wan Wan,

180
00:09:20,900 --> 00:09:21,900
tell me the truth.

181
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:25,000
What exactly is your purpose
to join the Drama Club?

182
00:09:29,300 --> 00:09:30,060
In fact,

183
00:09:31,190 --> 00:09:33,440
I have crush on the president
of the drama club.

184
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,550
He is very handsome.

185
00:09:36,790 --> 00:09:37,790
Believe me!

186
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,420
[To Li Jin Bu]

187
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:25,350
You are...

188
00:10:26,060 --> 00:10:28,170
You're the student who came
to report earlier, right?

189
00:10:29,270 --> 00:10:30,680
Hello!

190
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,640
Where is your relative?

191
00:10:31,730 --> 00:10:32,870
Is she getting better?

192
00:10:43,700 --> 00:10:45,270
She is okay now.

193
00:10:45,420 --> 00:10:47,050
Thanks to you
for putting us in the same dormitory.

194
00:10:47,070 --> 00:10:47,780
Thank you very much.

195
00:10:49,730 --> 00:10:50,530
You are welcome.

196
00:10:50,790 --> 00:10:51,650
I'm Fang Jin Han,

197
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:52,670
sophomore
in the Department of Chinese.

198
00:10:52,940 --> 00:10:54,750
If you two need any help,

199
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:55,870
you can come to me.

200
00:10:56,850 --> 00:10:57,830
Okay.

201
00:10:58,270 --> 00:10:59,540
I'll take this.

202
00:11:00,070 --> 00:11:00,690
Bye.

203
00:11:00,730 --> 00:11:01,530
Goodbye senior.

204
00:11:03,810 --> 00:11:04,850
Boss, checkout.

205
00:11:07,460 --> 00:11:08,460
Get up, relative.

206
00:11:19,830 --> 00:11:22,030
If you can't write the love letter,

207
00:11:22,470 --> 00:11:24,580
you can start from
what you are used to doing.

208
00:11:26,250 --> 00:11:27,660
Then I'll do what I did before.

209
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:29,580
I'll go straight over
and sit next to her.

210
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,430
Then you'll get the same result.

211
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:36,260
What should I do?

212
00:11:36,770 --> 00:11:39,290
Don't pester girls.

213
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:41,000
We are not kids.

214
00:11:41,090 --> 00:11:43,190
Pulling a girl's pigtails
doesn't work anymore.

215
00:11:44,330 --> 00:11:46,050
What you should do
is to accompany her.

216
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:47,320
Accompany, okay?

217
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,470
Don't show off your vocabulary.

218
00:11:49,610 --> 00:11:50,490
Be clear.

219
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:52,340
I mean,

220
00:11:52,780 --> 00:11:54,980
you should keep her company every day,

221
00:11:55,070 --> 00:11:55,950
but

222
00:11:56,230 --> 00:11:57,510
do not bother her.

223
00:11:58,280 --> 00:11:59,870
Look at her and be good to her.

224
00:12:00,660 --> 00:12:02,060
And don't ask for returning.

225
00:12:02,330 --> 00:12:03,330
That's it.

226
00:12:03,650 --> 00:12:04,820
Why am I so lowly?

227
00:12:06,350 --> 00:12:07,980
Then there's nothing I can do.

228
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:09,760
If you want to succeed,

229
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,140
then listen to me.

230
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:13,420
Will this work?

231
00:12:16,010 --> 00:12:17,160
Da Fan.

232
00:12:17,250 --> 00:12:18,150
Hello!

233
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,240
Hello!

234
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:40,300
Hi!

235
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,450
Milk.

236
00:12:58,740 --> 00:12:59,440
Here.

237
00:13:17,570 --> 00:13:19,770
[The Drama Club
of Lin Yang Teachers College]

238
00:13:21,930 --> 00:13:23,610
Who is the president

239
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:24,640
of the Drama Club?

240
00:13:24,710 --> 00:13:26,420
He's not here yet. Don't be impatient.

241
00:13:28,530 --> 00:13:29,230
Senior.

242
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:33,000
What are you doing here?

243
00:13:34,020 --> 00:13:35,260
Hello, senior.

244
00:13:36,750 --> 00:13:37,850
You know each other?

245
00:13:37,940 --> 00:13:38,970
We have met twice.

246
00:13:39,390 --> 00:13:41,050
You seem to have recovered
from your illness

247
00:13:41,230 --> 00:13:42,700
and are now able to join a club.

248
00:13:43,070 --> 00:13:44,190
That's great!

249
00:13:44,500 --> 00:13:45,680
What illness?

250
00:13:47,930 --> 00:13:48,910
Nothing.

251
00:13:49,290 --> 00:13:51,010
Let me introduce him to you.

252
00:13:51,050 --> 00:13:52,300
This is our president
of the Drama Club,

253
00:13:52,370 --> 00:13:53,320
Fang Jin Han.

254
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:54,540
He is one year older than us.

255
00:13:54,570 --> 00:13:56,620
He is recognized as the Prince Charming
of the Chinese Department.

256
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:58,840
He is also a senior officer
of the student union.

257
00:13:58,930 --> 00:14:00,510
It's just a little thing.
It's not worth mentioning.

258
00:14:00,610 --> 00:14:01,790
I just serve for everyone.

259
00:14:02,980 --> 00:14:03,780
By the way, Jin Han,

260
00:14:04,380 --> 00:14:07,220
all four of us
want to join the Drama Club.

261
00:14:08,310 --> 00:14:09,590
But I don't know

262
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:11,000
if the president will give us the chance.

263
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,050
Of course,

264
00:14:12,130 --> 00:14:13,010
anyone who is willing to join the club

265
00:14:13,050 --> 00:14:14,250
is more than welcome.

266
00:14:15,130 --> 00:14:16,120
Have a seat.

267
00:14:16,210 --> 00:14:17,440
I have something to deal with.

268
00:14:20,620 --> 00:14:21,460
What do you think?

269
00:14:22,030 --> 00:14:23,080
What do you think?

270
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:44,250
Does he like her?

271
00:14:57,890 --> 00:15:00,750
[No. 1 Students' Dormitory]

272
00:15:02,020 --> 00:15:02,950
Xiao!

273
00:15:09,370 --> 00:15:10,870
What's the matter?

274
00:15:11,130 --> 00:15:12,250
Nothing big.

275
00:15:12,890 --> 00:15:14,200
Then I'll go.

276
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:21,030
What's wrong with you two?

277
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:22,840
Why is this relationship getting worse?

278
00:15:23,460 --> 00:15:25,070
I have no idea.

279
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:27,730
I told her so much the other night,

280
00:15:27,820 --> 00:15:29,170
I thought it would work,

281
00:15:29,490 --> 00:15:31,080
but it didn't work at all.

282
00:15:33,390 --> 00:15:35,110
Then there's nothing I can do about it.

283
00:15:52,620 --> 00:15:55,540
What's wrong with you two?

284
00:15:57,290 --> 00:15:58,310
What do you think?

285
00:15:58,650 --> 00:16:00,770
I deliver milk to her
every day in their class.

286
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:02,650
Everyone thinks I'm a milkman now.

287
00:16:04,630 --> 00:16:05,590
How about you?

288
00:16:06,770 --> 00:16:08,070
I'm worse.

289
00:16:08,550 --> 00:16:10,550
We used to be so close in the past.

290
00:16:11,540 --> 00:16:13,900
Now we've gone back to strangers.

291
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:16,380
I can't even send the love letter
that I've worked so hard to write.

292
00:16:18,800 --> 00:16:20,470
You two are...

293
00:16:20,630 --> 00:16:22,860
What should I do to save you?

294
00:16:23,420 --> 00:16:25,150
Can you stop talking smack here?

295
00:16:25,470 --> 00:16:26,670
Find a way quickly.

296
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:28,980
Forget about the milk first.

297
00:16:30,040 --> 00:16:31,210
You should find a way

298
00:16:31,340 --> 00:16:32,620
to send your love letter.

299
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:33,540
And

300
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:35,250
you can't send it directly.

301
00:16:35,330 --> 00:16:36,210
Then what?

302
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:38,600
I'll deal with it.

303
00:16:45,070 --> 00:16:46,650
Don't you think they are strange?

304
00:16:47,430 --> 00:16:48,580
One doesn't drink milk

305
00:16:48,810 --> 00:16:49,780
and the other doesn't eat fruit.

306
00:16:50,170 --> 00:16:51,410
Don't you think they are pretencious?

307
00:16:51,890 --> 00:16:53,920
You're criticizing them
while eating their food.

308
00:16:54,010 --> 00:16:55,130
That's too much.

309
00:16:55,540 --> 00:16:57,060
I'm just reminding them

310
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:58,710
to cherish the good times of their youth.

311
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,730
Otherwise, when we get older,

312
00:17:00,870 --> 00:17:02,820
no men will be interested in us anymore.

313
00:17:03,860 --> 00:17:04,900
Same goes to you.

314
00:17:05,050 --> 00:17:06,530
Don't write letters all day.

315
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:07,640
Do the right thing.

316
00:17:08,170 --> 00:17:09,640
I am doing the right thing.

317
00:17:09,730 --> 00:17:11,700
You don't understand
the ambitions of literary youths.

318
00:17:11,780 --> 00:17:14,329
This is an exchange of ideas
between pen pals.

319
00:17:16,220 --> 00:17:17,010
Let me see,

320
00:17:17,099 --> 00:17:17,829
are there any love letters?

321
00:17:17,890 --> 00:17:19,040
Don't make a mess of it!

322
00:17:19,079 --> 00:17:20,630
I have to write back one by one.

323
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:23,160
You make it sound like a real business.

324
00:17:23,660 --> 00:17:24,619
All right, go to the class.

325
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,290
Who are you coming for?

326
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:31,800
Hello, I'm here to deliver a letter.

327
00:17:32,810 --> 00:17:34,360
Give it to the one inside.

328
00:17:35,620 --> 00:17:36,900
The letter...

329
00:17:36,990 --> 00:17:38,570
Give it to me. Thanks.

330
00:17:42,790 --> 00:17:44,140
Room 201...

331
00:17:44,910 --> 00:17:46,670
She should be Li Jinbu.

332
00:17:47,420 --> 00:17:48,470
Da Fan.

333
00:17:48,560 --> 00:17:49,440
Did she accept the letter?

334
00:17:49,580 --> 00:17:50,410
Yeah.

335
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:51,460
That girl said

336
00:17:51,550 --> 00:17:52,510
she was very happy.

337
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:54,180
That's good.

338
00:17:54,370 --> 00:17:54,860
Da Fan.

339
00:17:55,120 --> 00:17:57,560
You must be the hero
sent from heaven to save me.

340
00:17:57,670 --> 00:17:58,970
I'll treat you to a nice meal
when it's done.

341
00:17:59,080 --> 00:18:00,430
It's just a piece of cake.

342
00:18:00,530 --> 00:18:01,530
All right, I'll go.

343
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:02,150
Bye.

344
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:02,730
Bye.

345
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:05,190
There is a club rehearsal this evening.

346
00:18:05,370 --> 00:18:07,170
Let's try to get the role.

347
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:08,320
What club?

348
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:20,500
Here you are.

349
00:18:21,690 --> 00:18:22,620
What club?

350
00:18:22,710 --> 00:18:23,470
The Drama Club.

351
00:18:25,300 --> 00:18:26,440
The Drama Club.

352
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:27,940
You should go.

353
00:18:29,390 --> 00:18:30,140
Wait.

354
00:18:30,620 --> 00:18:31,910
Is it necessary?

355
00:18:32,020 --> 00:18:33,510
Of course.

356
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:34,970
Think about it.

357
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:38,920
The biggest problem is that
you don't communicate with each other.

358
00:18:39,030 --> 00:18:41,670
You should take this opportunity
to join the same club with her.

359
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:42,920
That way,

360
00:18:43,010 --> 00:18:45,040
you can communicate with each other
in a proper way.

361
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:54,390
It's been a few days.

362
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:56,200
Why is there still no message?

363
00:19:00,370 --> 00:19:00,970
Hello.

364
00:19:01,060 --> 00:19:01,740
Hello.

365
00:19:01,910 --> 00:19:02,740
This is Duan Xiao.

366
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,020
I'd like to talk to Li Jinbu.

367
00:19:04,330 --> 00:19:05,780
Hua, Duan Xiao is looking for you.

368
00:19:06,660 --> 00:19:08,070
Just say I am sleeping.

369
00:19:09,040 --> 00:19:10,000
Did you hear that?

370
00:19:10,050 --> 00:19:11,630
Do I need to repeat it?

371
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:14,900
No.

372
00:19:14,990 --> 00:19:15,550
Bye.

373
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:16,350
Bye.

374
00:19:18,230 --> 00:19:20,310
What's wrong?

375
00:19:21,660 --> 00:19:23,600
Did I write badly?

376
00:19:24,180 --> 00:19:26,490
[The Drama Club
of Lin Yang Teachers College]

377
00:19:26,490 --> 00:19:27,210
[Butterfly Lovers]

378
00:19:27,210 --> 00:19:27,920
Students,

379
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,410
two of the school's clubs
have been invited

380
00:19:29,700 --> 00:19:32,130
to take part in Student Arts Week,

381
00:19:32,290 --> 00:19:33,590
and our Drama Club

382
00:19:33,670 --> 00:19:34,850
is one of them!

383
00:19:34,950 --> 00:19:35,700
That's great!

384
00:19:36,850 --> 00:19:39,450
-What's up?
-It is a great opportunity.

385
00:19:40,540 --> 00:19:41,860
I've decided that

386
00:19:41,950 --> 00:19:43,950
our production is

387
00:19:44,040 --> 00:19:46,040
the classic love tragedy,

388
00:19:46,790 --> 00:19:47,710
"Butterfly Lovers".

389
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:48,630
Why does he come?

390
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:49,440
He...

391
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:50,960
He comes here to make fun of me.

392
00:19:51,050 --> 00:19:52,730
So, I'd like to
discuss the casting with you.

393
00:19:53,080 --> 00:19:54,530
The teacher suggested that

394
00:19:54,570 --> 00:19:56,170
I should play the role of Liang Shan Bo.

395
00:19:56,460 --> 00:19:57,730
As for Zhu Ying Tai,

396
00:19:58,010 --> 00:19:59,720
the teacher would like
to give this opportunity

397
00:19:59,900 --> 00:20:02,190
to those who are new
to the club this year.

398
00:20:02,740 --> 00:20:03,330
President,

399
00:20:03,680 --> 00:20:04,760
I think I can do this.

400
00:20:04,870 --> 00:20:05,880
Of course you can.

401
00:20:06,850 --> 00:20:07,690
But

402
00:20:07,770 --> 00:20:09,580
Zhu Ying Tai

403
00:20:09,820 --> 00:20:10,730
is a gallant lady...

404
00:20:10,810 --> 00:20:12,480
-with unique personality.
-Why are you coming?

405
00:20:12,570 --> 00:20:14,010
It's none of your business.

406
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:16,800
I think your appearance is a bit

407
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:17,840
on the feminine side

408
00:20:18,070 --> 00:20:19,540
and a bit

409
00:20:19,630 --> 00:20:21,360
out of character.

410
00:20:21,470 --> 00:20:22,430
What the hell are you doing again?

411
00:20:22,430 --> 00:20:24,980
-I can't hear you.
-I think...

412
00:20:28,450 --> 00:20:30,330
Li Jinbu can play her.

413
00:20:33,430 --> 00:20:34,390
It's you.

414
00:20:38,180 --> 00:20:38,840
What?

415
00:20:38,930 --> 00:20:39,540
All right,

416
00:20:39,630 --> 00:20:41,150
let's call it a day.

417
00:20:41,980 --> 00:20:42,590
Jinbu,

418
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:44,040
fighting!

419
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:54,920
What happened?

420
00:20:55,650 --> 00:20:56,390
Jinbu,

421
00:20:56,830 --> 00:20:57,550
fighting!

422
00:20:58,590 --> 00:20:59,830
Chen Jun He, wait!

423
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,800
What?

424
00:21:06,120 --> 00:21:07,440
What are you doing?

425
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:08,300
Me?

426
00:21:08,540 --> 00:21:10,500
I'm here for the club activity.

427
00:21:11,220 --> 00:21:12,410
There are so many clubs in the school.

428
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:13,540
Why you just have to join the Drama Club?

429
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:14,280
You...

430
00:21:14,390 --> 00:21:15,390
What are you doing here?

431
00:21:16,240 --> 00:21:17,070
You have no idea.

432
00:21:17,120 --> 00:21:18,880
I'm crazy about acting.

433
00:21:19,100 --> 00:21:20,540
I have no place

434
00:21:20,590 --> 00:21:21,270
to express

435
00:21:21,300 --> 00:21:22,970
my artistic cells, you know?

436
00:21:23,010 --> 00:21:24,380
Shame on you!

437
00:21:25,430 --> 00:21:26,150
I'm warning you

438
00:21:26,270 --> 00:21:27,750
don't do anything inexplicable again

439
00:21:27,810 --> 00:21:29,130
and end up getting me in trouble.

440
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:32,700
Li Qing Tong,

441
00:21:33,180 --> 00:21:35,010
everything I've done so far

442
00:21:35,350 --> 00:21:36,940
has not been done with the intention
of getting you into trouble.

443
00:21:37,660 --> 00:21:39,030
I have a clear conscience.

444
00:21:40,610 --> 00:21:41,100
You!

445
00:21:42,810 --> 00:21:44,620
You have a clear conscience?

446
00:21:57,820 --> 00:21:59,330
I have told you

447
00:21:59,580 --> 00:22:01,490
I'm not interested in playing that role

448
00:22:01,630 --> 00:22:03,470
and I don't want to join this club.

449
00:22:03,980 --> 00:22:06,130
It's hard to protect your home

450
00:22:06,230 --> 00:22:07,310
from thieves in your home!

451
00:22:07,820 --> 00:22:08,820
Just tell him you won't act,

452
00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:09,760
and recommend me.

453
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,200
I have already told him.

454
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:13,680
You told him specifically once more.

455
00:22:13,770 --> 00:22:14,570
Okay.

456
00:22:14,670 --> 00:22:15,910
I'll tell him tomorrow.

457
00:22:17,090 --> 00:22:18,170
Don't be angry.

458
00:22:19,550 --> 00:22:20,430
All right,

459
00:22:21,140 --> 00:22:22,210
reluctantly, I forgive you.

460
00:22:25,620 --> 00:22:27,340
Has the Swift Leg replied?

461
00:22:28,970 --> 00:22:29,720
Not yet.

462
00:22:31,480 --> 00:22:32,270
She

463
00:22:32,360 --> 00:22:33,720
probably just hasn't thought clearly yet.

464
00:22:36,710 --> 00:22:37,270
No.

465
00:22:38,030 --> 00:22:39,030
I'll have to ask her face to face.

466
00:22:39,180 --> 00:22:40,250
I'll die with the truth.

467
00:22:44,280 --> 00:22:46,080
Speaking of the devil.

468
00:22:57,570 --> 00:22:59,310
It's a great opportunity
to represent the school,

469
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:01,200
and the head of the school
takes it very seriously.

470
00:23:01,310 --> 00:23:03,190
I don't care about that.

471
00:23:03,330 --> 00:23:04,810
I join the club

472
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:06,480
just to keep Zhang Wan Wan company.

473
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:07,710
So,

474
00:23:08,210 --> 00:23:10,180
could you please
give this opportunity to her?

475
00:23:12,700 --> 00:23:13,450
All right.

476
00:23:14,330 --> 00:23:15,560
If you don't want to,

477
00:23:15,780 --> 00:23:16,570
I won't force you.

478
00:23:17,060 --> 00:23:18,330
Thank you for your understanding.

479
00:23:20,180 --> 00:23:20,860
What a shame.

480
00:23:21,690 --> 00:23:23,590
I had a time travel script that

481
00:23:23,700 --> 00:23:25,020
would have been perfect for you too.

482
00:23:26,270 --> 00:23:27,750
Time travel?

483
00:23:29,990 --> 00:23:31,310
Could you tell me about it?

484
00:23:32,370 --> 00:23:32,990
Okay.

485
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:34,710
It's like this.

486
00:23:35,460 --> 00:23:37,200
Have you seen "Back to Seventeen"?

487
00:23:37,430 --> 00:23:38,070
But

488
00:23:38,160 --> 00:23:39,580
my script

489
00:23:39,670 --> 00:23:40,870
is darker.

490
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:43,600
Because he's going back in time
to kill his own father.

491
00:23:50,940 --> 00:23:52,130
Will he come back?

492
00:23:52,610 --> 00:23:53,690
I don't know.

493
00:23:53,750 --> 00:23:55,240
What would you do if you were him?

494
00:23:55,600 --> 00:23:56,850
I have no idea, neither.

495
00:23:58,370 --> 00:23:59,500
Now I know

496
00:23:59,650 --> 00:24:01,730
why does she suddenly ignore me.

497
00:24:02,610 --> 00:24:03,640
It is because...

498
00:24:07,750 --> 00:24:08,500
To be honest,

499
00:24:08,630 --> 00:24:10,690
I would have rushed in if I were you.

500
00:24:11,570 --> 00:24:13,250
But you have to consider
the Swift Leg's personality.

501
00:24:14,040 --> 00:24:15,690
She responds to persuasion
but not to force.

502
00:24:15,970 --> 00:24:17,290
If you had indeed rushed in

503
00:24:17,490 --> 00:24:18,440
and quarreled with her,

504
00:24:18,570 --> 00:24:19,720
that's going to be the end.

505
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,120
What should I do?

506
00:24:21,430 --> 00:24:22,630
Do I just accept it?

507
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:23,130
No,

508
00:24:23,230 --> 00:24:24,430
you can't accept it.

509
00:24:26,090 --> 00:24:27,770
Let's go back and talk to Da Fan about it.

510
00:24:27,850 --> 00:24:28,850
He has more ideas.

511
00:24:33,530 --> 00:24:34,760
Where are you going?

512
00:24:38,060 --> 00:24:39,780
You should go back now.

513
00:24:41,850 --> 00:24:43,200
It's a great chat.

514
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:44,690
Next time we shall

515
00:24:44,970 --> 00:24:46,070
time travel again.

516
00:24:47,130 --> 00:24:47,870
Well,

517
00:24:47,960 --> 00:24:49,330
are you free tomorrow?

518
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:51,000
Would you like to have dinner with me?

519
00:24:51,350 --> 00:24:52,640
I can't make it tomorrow.

520
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:54,000
I have something to do tomorrow.

521
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:56,230
All right.

522
00:24:56,500 --> 00:24:58,410
Then we'll meet again when you're free.

523
00:24:59,620 --> 00:25:00,720
Goodbye.

524
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:04,830
Goodbye.

525
00:25:15,110 --> 00:25:16,070
What are you doing?

526
00:25:16,910 --> 00:25:17,900
Who is him?

527
00:25:19,020 --> 00:25:21,310
He's the president of the Drama Club.

528
00:25:21,490 --> 00:25:22,200
What's wrong?

529
00:25:22,760 --> 00:25:23,950
What's your relationship?

530
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:25,770
We have no relationship.

531
00:25:28,180 --> 00:25:29,320
Then tell me honestly,

532
00:25:29,850 --> 00:25:31,930
are you looking for excuses
to break up with me

533
00:25:32,310 --> 00:25:33,390
because of him?

534
00:25:35,390 --> 00:25:36,800
What does break up mean?

535
00:25:37,110 --> 00:25:38,300
Have we been together?

536
00:25:38,380 --> 00:25:39,750
Just answer me. Is it yes

537
00:25:40,250 --> 00:25:40,940
or no?

538
00:25:41,020 --> 00:25:41,740
Yes

539
00:25:43,510 --> 00:25:44,300
or no,

540
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:45,920
it's my business.

541
00:25:46,350 --> 00:25:47,230
What does it matter to you?

542
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:48,390
Of course, it matters to me.

543
00:25:50,400 --> 00:25:51,840
It's come to this,

544
00:25:52,780 --> 00:25:54,270
I've nothing to hide.

545
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:56,600
After all, the whole world
knows I like you.

546
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,090
I'll say it plainly today

547
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:01,410
I, Duan Xiao, like Li Jinbu.

548
00:26:01,770 --> 00:26:04,680
I, Duan Xiao,
am destined to be nice to Li Jinbu.

549
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:06,030
I, Duan Xiao,

550
00:26:06,100 --> 00:26:08,110
want to be Li Jinbu's boyfriend.

551
00:26:08,300 --> 00:26:09,710
Nobody can stop me.

552
00:26:12,750 --> 00:26:14,290
I've always listened to you before,

553
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,260
but today I'll be bossy for once.

554
00:26:18,730 --> 00:26:21,010
I forbid you to spend all day with him.

555
00:26:21,380 --> 00:26:23,460
I should be the one there for you
when you need help.

556
00:26:23,550 --> 00:26:24,470
Not him!

557
00:26:27,140 --> 00:26:29,380
If I see you stay with him again,

558
00:26:29,950 --> 00:26:30,590
I will...

559
00:26:30,610 --> 00:26:31,450
You will do what?

560
00:26:32,330 --> 00:26:34,630
I will break his leg.

561
00:26:35,320 --> 00:26:37,120
Are you crazy?

562
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:39,680
You.

563
00:26:39,760 --> 00:26:40,840
Just talk if you want.

564
00:26:40,860 --> 00:26:42,360
Why did you hit me?

565
00:26:42,450 --> 00:26:44,890
Is this what you have learned
from Chen Jun He?

566
00:26:45,040 --> 00:26:46,090
I'm so mad at you!

567
00:26:46,310 --> 00:26:46,900
What?

568
00:26:47,770 --> 00:26:49,740
You're the one who make me mad.

569
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:54,320
I haven't finished.

570
00:26:54,420 --> 00:26:55,540
What do you mean?

571
00:26:58,640 --> 00:27:00,440
I'll break his leg!

572
00:27:02,550 --> 00:27:04,490
Where did he learn this?

573
00:27:05,020 --> 00:27:06,060
He's crazy.

574
00:27:06,910 --> 00:27:07,830
What's wrong with her?

575
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:08,790
I don't know.

576
00:27:09,320 --> 00:27:10,900
As soon as she came back,
she was like this.

577
00:27:11,090 --> 00:27:11,930
I'm fine.

578
00:27:12,010 --> 00:27:13,130
Don't stand there, you three.

579
00:27:13,550 --> 00:27:15,300
She can hear us even in such a low voice!

580
00:27:16,990 --> 00:27:18,390
Are the oranges good?

581
00:27:19,670 --> 00:27:20,800
How does she see that?

582
00:27:26,530 --> 00:27:27,380
Dude,

583
00:27:27,550 --> 00:27:28,920
when it comes to girls,

584
00:27:29,100 --> 00:27:31,540
you have to be a hard-ass.

585
00:27:31,630 --> 00:27:33,780
You've known each other for so long.

586
00:27:33,840 --> 00:27:35,360
It can't really be a game over.

587
00:27:36,060 --> 00:27:36,980
Just do it.

588
00:27:37,090 --> 00:27:37,670
All the best.

589
00:27:37,930 --> 00:27:38,600
It'll be fine.

590
00:27:39,730 --> 00:27:40,220
Go!

591
00:27:44,710 --> 00:27:45,980
Why does he come again?

592
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:52,710
Jin Bu.

593
00:27:52,800 --> 00:27:53,420
Jin Han.

594
00:27:53,510 --> 00:27:54,450
Anything?

595
00:27:55,710 --> 00:27:56,670
Here.

596
00:28:03,890 --> 00:28:05,650
It's a real game over.

597
00:28:06,620 --> 00:28:08,160
Wait for me.

598
00:28:09,300 --> 00:28:10,790
Why do you give me flowers?

599
00:28:11,590 --> 00:28:12,440
Flowers...

600
00:28:12,550 --> 00:28:13,700
It's for

601
00:28:14,190 --> 00:28:15,790
the girl I like.

602
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:17,520
Jin Han,

603
00:28:18,760 --> 00:28:20,080
stop kidding.

604
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:21,450
No, I'm not kidding.

605
00:28:23,650 --> 00:28:25,140
Sorry, I can't accept it.

606
00:28:25,230 --> 00:28:26,070
Please take it back.

607
00:28:29,150 --> 00:28:30,390
I'll get going now.

608
00:28:39,350 --> 00:28:41,110
Didn't he say that
he would come here early?

609
00:28:41,550 --> 00:28:42,700
Where did he go?

610
00:28:50,570 --> 00:28:51,610
Bad news!

611
00:28:52,380 --> 00:28:54,020
Something big happened!

612
00:28:54,710 --> 00:28:55,910
Bad news!

613
00:28:55,980 --> 00:28:56,740
What's wrong?

614
00:28:57,480 --> 00:28:59,040
I just met Chen Jun He downstairs.

615
00:28:59,130 --> 00:29:00,710
He said that Duan Xiao was angry with you.

616
00:29:00,820 --> 00:29:01,460
He also said

617
00:29:01,570 --> 00:29:03,110
Duan Xiao would never come back.

618
00:29:03,620 --> 00:29:04,820
Why does he mad at me?

619
00:29:05,360 --> 00:29:06,640
I don't know either.

620
00:29:06,900 --> 00:29:07,580
He said...

621
00:29:08,100 --> 00:29:10,420
He saw that you were close to another boy.

622
00:29:10,860 --> 00:29:11,490
He also said that

623
00:29:12,030 --> 00:29:13,550
you accepted other's flowers.

624
00:29:14,730 --> 00:29:15,810
Now I see.

625
00:29:16,050 --> 00:29:17,320
Is he a fool?

626
00:29:17,410 --> 00:29:18,860
Didn't he see me returning the flower?

627
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:21,580
Well, whatever.

628
00:29:22,560 --> 00:29:24,030
Wait! What flowers?

629
00:29:24,980 --> 00:29:26,080
It is just a misunderstanding.

630
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:27,520
I have returned the flowers.

631
00:29:27,800 --> 00:29:29,160
Someone gave you flowers?

632
00:29:29,620 --> 00:29:30,620
Who was that?

633
00:29:34,700 --> 00:29:35,940
It's a shame.

634
00:29:36,730 --> 00:29:39,410
After a careful thought, Li Jin Bu

635
00:29:40,060 --> 00:29:42,230
thinks that she is not a good fit
for the role.

636
00:29:42,450 --> 00:29:43,370
I think

637
00:29:43,590 --> 00:29:44,880
it is abrupt for me

638
00:29:44,970 --> 00:29:46,320
to name the actress.

639
00:29:46,980 --> 00:29:48,070
So, I suggest that

640
00:29:48,330 --> 00:29:49,850
everyone who wishes to participate

641
00:29:49,940 --> 00:29:51,820
will each prepare a short clip.

642
00:29:51,910 --> 00:29:53,110
It'll be decided through voting.

643
00:29:53,180 --> 00:29:53,910
What do you think?

644
00:29:54,150 --> 00:29:54,900
That's great!

645
00:29:59,780 --> 00:30:01,940
[Butterfly Lovers]

646
00:30:02,040 --> 00:30:03,380
[Describe the world
with few lines on the stage]

647
00:30:03,470 --> 00:30:05,400
[The Drama Club
of Lin Yang Teachers College]

648
00:30:06,120 --> 00:30:07,920
I think you look quite like Zhu Ying Tai.

649
00:30:08,010 --> 00:30:09,390
Don't you think she has the heroic look?

650
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:13,780
Since Li Jin Bu
is not going to participate,

651
00:30:13,860 --> 00:30:15,170
I'll play Zhu Yingtai.

652
00:30:15,780 --> 00:30:16,810
Who do you two want to play?

653
00:30:18,350 --> 00:30:19,630
Me? I'll play the little schoolboy.

654
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,790
Can I play Liang Shan Bo?

655
00:30:23,460 --> 00:30:25,660
Maybe you can.

656
00:30:25,740 --> 00:30:27,470
The problem is I'm not good at it.

657
00:30:27,550 --> 00:30:29,260
Why don't we get a boy to play it?

658
00:30:30,940 --> 00:30:32,500
Where can we get one?

659
00:30:37,360 --> 00:30:38,210
How about me?

660
00:30:50,950 --> 00:30:51,920
Here, it's your turn.

661
00:30:54,030 --> 00:30:55,520
Look, Duan Xiao...

662
00:30:56,100 --> 00:30:57,690
He didn't answer my calls
for the past two days.

663
00:30:57,770 --> 00:30:58,730
Why?

664
00:31:00,280 --> 00:31:02,010
He needs time to recover.

665
00:31:02,100 --> 00:31:03,450
Just leave him alone.

666
00:31:03,930 --> 00:31:04,450
By the way,

667
00:31:05,080 --> 00:31:07,040
is everything okay with your club?

668
00:31:07,320 --> 00:31:08,250
Let me ask you a question.

669
00:31:08,510 --> 00:31:10,670
Ma Wen Cai...

670
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:11,760
Do you know who is he?

671
00:31:12,250 --> 00:31:14,010
Are you going to play Ma Wen Cai?

672
00:31:15,330 --> 00:31:16,730
That's the role they assigned to me.

673
00:31:16,910 --> 00:31:18,480
Judging from the lines,

674
00:31:18,780 --> 00:31:20,710
he doesn't seem like a nice guy.

675
00:31:21,150 --> 00:31:22,790
I think it suits you.

676
00:31:23,470 --> 00:31:24,090
Really?

677
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:29,100
Don't be sad, young lady.

678
00:31:29,190 --> 00:31:31,150
Young Master Liang will come for you.

679
00:31:32,010 --> 00:31:32,810
No matter what happens,

680
00:31:33,150 --> 00:31:35,310
I won't marry Ma Wen Cai.

681
00:31:51,770 --> 00:31:52,760
Ma Wen Cai!

682
00:31:53,300 --> 00:31:55,030
Stop dreaming.

683
00:31:55,120 --> 00:31:57,070
She won't marry you!

684
00:32:00,460 --> 00:32:01,340
Why?

685
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:04,700
I am Zhu Ying Tai.

686
00:32:07,210 --> 00:32:08,320
Because she

687
00:32:08,610 --> 00:32:10,540
hates a playboy like you!

688
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:11,760
You're a bad guy!

689
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:14,200
She only likes scholarly man.

690
00:32:48,650 --> 00:32:50,100
You like that nerd, right?

691
00:32:50,630 --> 00:32:51,830
Don't you think that I don't know.

692
00:32:52,260 --> 00:32:53,460
You should follow the lines.

693
00:32:53,770 --> 00:32:55,120
I'm Zhu Ying Tai.

694
00:32:55,520 --> 00:32:56,880
You're talking to the wrong person.

695
00:32:57,100 --> 00:32:58,740
Is that nerd really that good?

696
00:32:59,120 --> 00:33:00,680
I'm better than him at anything
except learning.

697
00:33:00,910 --> 00:33:02,180
Has he ever fought for you?

698
00:33:02,570 --> 00:33:04,840
Did he attend the same school as you
just to be with you?

699
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:06,650
Why am I wrong?

700
00:33:06,800 --> 00:33:08,410
Why am I the bad guy?

701
00:33:08,900 --> 00:33:09,710
I know.

702
00:33:09,820 --> 00:33:10,960
I know that you are a couple.

703
00:33:11,390 --> 00:33:12,270
You're the Butterfly Lovers.

704
00:33:12,850 --> 00:33:15,170
I, Ma Wencai,
am just a lunatic who interferes.

705
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:17,820
But I also have someone I like

706
00:33:17,870 --> 00:33:19,510
and someone I want to pursue.

707
00:33:20,110 --> 00:33:21,030
Just like now.

708
00:33:21,910 --> 00:33:23,030
Where is the nerd?

709
00:33:23,900 --> 00:33:25,850
I'm the one
who have been keeping you company!

710
00:33:27,500 --> 00:33:28,900
Even if you don't like me,

711
00:33:29,470 --> 00:33:30,520
it's okay,

712
00:33:30,860 --> 00:33:32,330
I don't regret it!

713
00:33:39,510 --> 00:33:40,390
Bravo!

714
00:33:40,700 --> 00:33:42,900
This was the best performance
I've seen today.

715
00:33:43,390 --> 00:33:44,860
Zhu Ying Tai and Ma Wen Cai

716
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:46,200
will be played by them.

717
00:33:46,290 --> 00:33:47,460
Do you agree?

718
00:33:47,480 --> 00:33:48,550
Yes.

719
00:33:48,630 --> 00:33:49,480
Jin Han.

720
00:33:50,190 --> 00:33:51,750
I am Zhu Ying Tai.

721
00:33:54,870 --> 00:33:56,630
There's always another chance.

722
00:33:57,200 --> 00:33:58,520
You can play Zhu Ying Tai next time.

723
00:33:58,830 --> 00:33:59,730
This all for today.

724
00:33:59,840 --> 00:34:00,920
You may leave now.

725
00:34:03,500 --> 00:34:04,220
Wan Wan!

726
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:05,370
Wan Wan!

727
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:15,610
Chen Jun He.

728
00:34:19,690 --> 00:34:20,389
Well...

729
00:34:20,469 --> 00:34:21,550
The president just asked me

730
00:34:21,630 --> 00:34:24,350
to go shopping for some costumes
and props this weekend.

731
00:34:25,290 --> 00:34:27,290
He said it would be better
to get a guy together.

732
00:34:32,010 --> 00:34:33,090
Are you going?

733
00:34:33,170 --> 00:34:35,050
If you don't go, I'll find someone else.

734
00:34:51,889 --> 00:34:53,170
[Good job, dude.]

735
00:34:53,260 --> 00:34:55,010
[Did you know that you've broken the ice?]

736
00:34:55,110 --> 00:34:57,100
[This is
a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.]

737
00:34:57,130 --> 00:34:58,790
[Say something nice,]

738
00:34:58,850 --> 00:35:00,290
[and show your concern for her.]

739
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:08,570
Are you thirsty?

740
00:35:09,900 --> 00:35:10,940
I have water.

741
00:35:15,830 --> 00:35:17,190
Are you cold?

742
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:21,750
I have more clothes on than you.

743
00:35:25,640 --> 00:35:26,170
Wait.

744
00:35:26,210 --> 00:35:28,650
Don't you have any discomfort?

745
00:35:30,480 --> 00:35:32,190
Why do you curse me?

746
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:34,600
Do I have to be uncomfortable?

747
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:47,250
I crave roasted sweet potatoes.

748
00:35:49,840 --> 00:35:52,440
Where could I find sweet potatoes
for sale in this cold weather?

749
00:35:55,740 --> 00:35:56,620
Forget it.

750
00:35:57,850 --> 00:35:58,650
Fine.

751
00:35:58,740 --> 00:35:59,330
All right.

752
00:35:59,430 --> 00:36:00,670
I'll find it to you.

753
00:36:14,350 --> 00:36:15,490
I haven't been out much

754
00:36:16,200 --> 00:36:17,560
since I have been here.

755
00:36:20,690 --> 00:36:22,310
When we have time,

756
00:36:22,580 --> 00:36:23,990
we can go out together

757
00:36:24,820 --> 00:36:26,420
to enjoy the city scenery.

758
00:36:32,040 --> 00:36:33,540
I said we can hang out sometimes.

759
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:37,970
Okay.

760
00:36:38,370 --> 00:36:39,440
Anytime.

761
00:36:46,070 --> 00:36:46,910
What are you doing?

762
00:36:47,220 --> 00:36:48,610
What are you two doing?

763
00:36:51,880 --> 00:36:53,290
Mind your own business, kid.

764
00:36:53,380 --> 00:36:55,000
Why are you so mean to him?

765
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:56,830
He wants to wet you with coke.

766
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:59,530
-Are you two a couple?
-What?

767
00:37:00,200 --> 00:37:02,540
You look like a couple.

768
00:37:02,620 --> 00:37:04,290
Stop interfering in our business.

769
00:37:04,330 --> 00:37:05,580
Just turn around.

770
00:37:05,700 --> 00:37:07,460
Don't be so mean to kid.

771
00:37:08,690 --> 00:37:10,510
I don't want to talk to him.

772
00:37:10,760 --> 00:37:12,790
I just want to talk to you, okay?

773
00:37:12,910 --> 00:37:13,510
Okay.

774
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:14,860
What do you want to say?

775
00:37:15,330 --> 00:37:17,770
You look like a snail.

776
00:37:18,500 --> 00:37:20,430
Do you know how to talk, little punk?

777
00:37:21,360 --> 00:37:22,680
Don't be so mean to him.

778
00:37:23,210 --> 00:37:26,370
The guy next to you looks like a rat.

779
00:37:27,160 --> 00:37:28,950
I think you look like a toad.

780
00:37:29,040 --> 00:37:30,110
You look like an earthworm!

781
00:37:30,200 --> 00:37:31,060
You look like a mosquito!

782
00:37:31,160 --> 00:37:32,550
You look like an earthworm!

783
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:33,480
You look like a mosquito!

784
00:37:36,230 --> 00:37:38,020
You look like a shithead.

785
00:37:38,200 --> 00:37:40,080
I think you look more like a shithead!

786
00:37:45,780 --> 00:37:47,210
Are you an idiot?

787
00:37:47,300 --> 00:37:48,770
Why did you argue with a kid?

788
00:37:48,860 --> 00:37:49,730
I don't care.

789
00:37:49,830 --> 00:37:50,710
He's bullying you.

790
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:53,140
Childish.

791
00:37:53,230 --> 00:37:54,060
Go away.

792
00:37:57,400 --> 00:37:58,890
Are you angry?

793
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,290
Narrow-minded.

794
00:38:51,870 --> 00:38:53,220
You're really something.

795
00:38:53,310 --> 00:38:54,420
Duan Xiao.

796
00:38:54,510 --> 00:38:56,410
You really didn't get back to me.

797
00:38:56,500 --> 00:38:57,780
I'll never talk to you again!

798
00:39:00,890 --> 00:39:03,000
He's busy as it's end of term.

799
00:39:03,040 --> 00:39:03,980
Winter holiday is coming.

800
00:39:04,010 --> 00:39:05,410
I'm sure he'll come for you
over winter holiday.

801
00:39:18,750 --> 00:39:20,600
It took us so much of effort
to buy the clothes

802
00:39:20,690 --> 00:39:22,010
but we didn't wear any of the clothes.

803
00:39:23,460 --> 00:39:24,620
I've told you.

804
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:26,840
Fang Jin Han
is not a reliable person at all.

805
00:39:27,150 --> 00:39:28,840
He said we can get great recommendation

806
00:39:29,160 --> 00:39:30,360
but we get nothing in the end.

807
00:39:31,550 --> 00:39:34,070
So you have nowhere else
to stir up trouble, Ma Wen Cai.

808
00:39:35,510 --> 00:39:36,070
It's fine.

809
00:39:36,970 --> 00:39:39,610
You, Zhu Ying Tai, don't have a chance
to be with Liang Shan Bo.

810
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:49,290
[Exit]

811
00:39:49,290 --> 00:39:52,050
Train No. 6231.

812
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:53,910
I can't see them, did you see them?

813
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:55,040
Here! Here!

814
00:39:58,830 --> 00:39:59,850
My girl.

815
00:39:59,890 --> 00:40:01,250
Dad! Mom!

816
00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:02,840
My girl.

817
00:40:03,810 --> 00:40:05,260
Give me your luggage.

818
00:40:05,350 --> 00:40:06,090
Mr Li!

819
00:40:06,580 --> 00:40:07,770
I miss you so much.

820
00:40:07,850 --> 00:40:09,000
You are thin, my girl.

821
00:40:09,090 --> 00:40:09,610
Go.

822
00:40:09,660 --> 00:40:10,560
Let's go.

823
00:40:10,580 --> 00:40:10,900
Jin Bu.

824
00:40:10,930 --> 00:40:11,420
Mrs. Li.

825
00:40:11,460 --> 00:40:12,410
Are you cold?

826
00:40:12,500 --> 00:40:13,130
No.

827
00:40:13,790 --> 00:40:14,990
Here comes the fish.

828
00:40:16,210 --> 00:40:17,460
Eat more, girl.

829
00:40:20,970 --> 00:40:21,720
Girl.

830
00:40:22,260 --> 00:40:23,850
Did you go to university

831
00:40:23,990 --> 00:40:25,230
or go to be a refugee?

832
00:40:25,500 --> 00:40:27,820
It's because my mother's cooking
is too delicious.

833
00:40:27,920 --> 00:40:29,860
It's a hundred times better
than our canteen food.

834
00:40:30,060 --> 00:40:30,900
No, it's ten thousand times better.

835
00:40:31,130 --> 00:40:32,230
Really?

836
00:40:32,580 --> 00:40:33,860
I'm not fooled.

837
00:40:34,650 --> 00:40:35,840
Mr and Mrs Li.

838
00:40:35,890 --> 00:40:37,880
We bought you presents with our savings.

839
00:40:37,950 --> 00:40:39,100
See if you like it.

840
00:40:40,100 --> 00:40:40,900
Of course we like it.

841
00:40:41,020 --> 00:40:42,610
We love everything you buy.

842
00:40:42,660 --> 00:40:43,840
What a waste of money.

843
00:40:43,930 --> 00:40:45,430
They're sincere.

844
00:40:45,470 --> 00:40:46,840
What can they buy?

845
00:40:47,510 --> 00:40:48,150
See?

846
00:40:48,200 --> 00:40:48,720
I've told you.

847
00:40:48,730 --> 00:40:49,650
It's not worth the price. Look.

848
00:40:51,500 --> 00:40:52,740
It's indeed a bit expensive.

849
00:40:55,720 --> 00:40:56,650
Let me try.

850
00:41:00,830 --> 00:41:01,590
How is it?

851
00:41:01,880 --> 00:41:02,840
Is it nice?

852
00:41:02,970 --> 00:41:03,770
It's nice.

853
00:41:03,860 --> 00:41:04,550
It looks good.

854
00:41:04,790 --> 00:41:06,080
-Here, Hua.
-You haven't even looked.

855
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:07,120
Thank you uncle.

856
00:41:07,210 --> 00:41:09,240
You guys are working together
to make me angry.

857
00:41:09,450 --> 00:41:10,670
My mum looks good in everything!

858
00:41:10,760 --> 00:41:12,530
-Certainly.
-She looks good in everything!

859
00:41:14,820 --> 00:41:15,660
All right.

860
00:41:16,400 --> 00:41:18,010
I like the color.

861
00:41:18,820 --> 00:41:20,270
And the sleeves look just right to me too.

862
00:41:20,530 --> 00:41:21,080
Look.

863
00:41:21,170 --> 00:41:22,090
It's suitable.

864
00:41:29,390 --> 00:41:30,420
Fatty!

865
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:31,410
Tong!

866
00:41:37,170 --> 00:41:37,780
Hua.

867
00:41:40,300 --> 00:41:41,410
How's going on?

868
00:41:41,490 --> 00:41:43,090
What about the south?

869
00:41:43,770 --> 00:41:44,560
Don't even mention it.

870
00:41:44,610 --> 00:41:45,550
It's just the way it is.

871
00:41:45,660 --> 00:41:47,160
The main problem is that
I'm not used to the food here.

872
00:41:47,250 --> 00:41:49,350
The quantity is too small to make me full.

873
00:41:49,810 --> 00:41:50,760
My place is fine.

874
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:52,200
It's not cold in the winter.

875
00:41:52,310 --> 00:41:54,730
And I stay right next to the sea
and it is beautiful.

876
00:41:54,820 --> 00:41:56,280
I wish I stay beside the sea!

877
00:41:56,370 --> 00:41:57,960
I've never even seen it.

878
00:41:58,030 --> 00:41:59,460
You can come and pay me a visit.

879
00:41:59,550 --> 00:42:02,140
Jinhai welcomes you.

880
00:42:03,700 --> 00:42:04,500
Hua.

881
00:42:04,540 --> 00:42:05,340
What's wrong with you?

882
00:42:05,380 --> 00:42:06,740
Why do you look sad?

883
00:42:08,190 --> 00:42:09,240
Where is Xiao?

884
00:42:09,710 --> 00:42:10,580
Children,

885
00:42:10,660 --> 00:42:11,570
the dumplings are ready.

886
00:42:11,620 --> 00:42:12,900
The dumplings are on me.

887
00:42:13,210 --> 00:42:13,650
Eat up.

888
00:42:13,690 --> 00:42:14,490
Thank you.

889
00:42:14,790 --> 00:42:15,230
Wait.

890
00:42:15,280 --> 00:42:16,420
When will Xiao be here?

891
00:42:16,510 --> 00:42:17,310
Shut up.

892
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:27,760
You're still in a cold war?

893
00:42:32,650 --> 00:42:34,730
Fang Jin Han

894
00:42:35,030 --> 00:42:36,420
looks like a thief.

895
00:42:36,500 --> 00:42:38,020
I know that he's not a good person
at first glance.

896
00:42:38,290 --> 00:42:39,640
But I'm telling you, don't worry.

897
00:42:39,730 --> 00:42:42,110
I don't think
Li Jin bu will fall in love with him.

898
00:42:42,200 --> 00:42:44,230
Think about the environment
in which Li Jin Bu grew up.

899
00:42:44,310 --> 00:42:45,120
Right?

900
00:42:45,210 --> 00:42:46,530
Who is she with all day?

901
00:42:46,610 --> 00:42:47,370
Duan Xiao.

902
00:42:47,460 --> 00:42:48,240
Chen Jun He.

903
00:42:48,330 --> 00:42:50,960
Those are
the most handsome men in Tieyuan.

904
00:42:51,050 --> 00:42:52,250
She won't fall in love with him.

905
00:42:52,330 --> 00:42:53,170
Don't worry.

906
00:42:56,370 --> 00:42:56,930
Well.

907
00:42:57,460 --> 00:42:58,540
What are you going to do next

908
00:42:59,510 --> 00:43:00,390
about you two?

909
00:43:02,880 --> 00:43:04,000
I think we both

910
00:43:04,510 --> 00:43:05,580
need time

911
00:43:05,670 --> 00:43:06,420
to calm down.

912
00:43:07,380 --> 00:43:08,220
We'll not see each other

913
00:43:09,760 --> 00:43:10,520
and take a break.

914
00:43:13,970 --> 00:43:14,890
What a mess!

915
00:43:16,120 --> 00:43:17,820
I used to have no hope,

916
00:43:17,930 --> 00:43:19,430
but we are getting closer and closer.

917
00:43:19,510 --> 00:43:20,990
You used to be
just one step away from her

918
00:43:21,850 --> 00:43:23,680
but now you're
on the edge of breaking up.

919
00:43:26,250 --> 00:43:28,160
You should take the opportunity
to confess your love.

920
00:43:28,250 --> 00:43:29,160
Strike while the iron is hot.

921
00:43:30,160 --> 00:43:30,690
Come on.

922
00:43:31,390 --> 00:43:32,590
Best wishes for your success.

923
00:43:33,080 --> 00:43:34,400
Life goes on.

924
00:43:44,460 --> 00:43:47,230
[Express train from Tieyuan to Linyang]

925
00:44:08,310 --> 00:44:08,870
Wait.

926
00:44:09,280 --> 00:44:11,000
Why are you taking me here?

927
00:44:11,530 --> 00:44:13,400
It's a new academic year.

928
00:44:13,500 --> 00:44:14,960
I think it's your time.

929
00:44:15,050 --> 00:44:15,780
What time?

930
00:44:16,320 --> 00:44:17,760
It's the time to confess your love.

931
00:44:19,270 --> 00:44:20,150
To who?

932
00:44:20,720 --> 00:44:21,430
Who else?

933
00:44:21,520 --> 00:44:22,520
To me?

934
00:44:22,740 --> 00:44:24,060
Li Qing Tong, of course.

935
00:44:25,780 --> 00:44:27,130
This is going too fast.

936
00:44:27,440 --> 00:44:28,790
It's not fast at all.

937
00:44:28,900 --> 00:44:29,620
Think about it.

938
00:44:30,020 --> 00:44:32,090
You got on so well with her last term.

939
00:44:32,180 --> 00:44:33,590
She had even asked you out.

940
00:44:33,780 --> 00:44:35,540
Confess to her now while the iron is hot.

941
00:44:38,050 --> 00:44:39,210
I've found a right place for you.

942
00:44:40,120 --> 00:44:41,620
It's up to you to act or not.

943
00:44:48,920 --> 00:44:49,510
Li Qing Tong,

944
00:44:52,310 --> 00:44:54,550
would you please be my girlfriend?
